    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreationDate], [p].[CreatorId], [p].[Description], [p].[Images], [p].[PostStatusId], [p].[Title], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreationDate] AS [CreationDate0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0]
    FROM [Post] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [p].[CreatorId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CommentBody], [c0].[CreationDate], [c0].[CreatorId], [c0].[PostId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[Avatar], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[Gender], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[Name], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[CreatorId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[PostId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

) AS [t]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ChatId], [t0].[CreationDate], [t0].[SenderId], [t1].[ChatsId], [t1].[MembersId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AccessFailedCount], [t1].[Avatar], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t1].[Email], [t1].[EmailConfirmed], [t1].[Gender], [t1].[LockoutEnabled], [t1].[LockoutEnd], [t1].[Name], [t1].[NormalizedEmail], [t1].[NormalizedUserName], [t1].[PasswordHash], [t1].[PhoneNumber], [t1].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t1].[SecurityStamp], [t1].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t1].[UserName]
FROM [Chat] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Body], [t].[ChatId], [t].[CreationDate], [t].[SenderId]
    FROM (
        SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Body], [m].[ChatId], [m].[CreationDate], [m].[SenderId], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [m].[ChatId] ORDER BY [m].[CreationDate] DESC) AS [row]
        FROM [Message] AS [m]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[ChatId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[ChatsId], [u].[MembersId], [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [UserChats] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [u].[MembersId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[ChatsId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [UserChats] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [u0].[MembersId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ([c].[Id] = [u0].[ChatsId]) AND ([a0].[Id] = @__entity_equality_user_0_Id)) AND ((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Message] AS [m0]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = [m0].[ChatId]) > 0)
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[ChatId], [t0].[CreationDate] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t1].[ChatsId], [t1].[MembersId], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ChatId], [t0].[CreationDate], [t0].[SenderId], [t1].[ChatsId], [t1].[MembersId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AccessFailedCount], [t1].[Avatar], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t1].[Email], [t1].[EmailConfirmed], [t1].[Gender], [t1].[LockoutEnabled], [t1].[LockoutEnd], [t1].[Name], [t1].[NormalizedEmail], [t1].[NormalizedUserName], [t1].[PasswordHash], [t1].[PhoneNumber], [t1].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t1].[SecurityStamp], [t1].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t1].[UserName]
FROM [Chat] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Body], [t].[ChatId], [t].[CreationDate], [t].[SenderId]
    FROM (
        SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Body], [m].[ChatId], [m].[CreationDate], [m].[SenderId], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [m].[ChatId] ORDER BY [m].[CreationDate] DESC) AS [row]
        FROM [Message] AS [m]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[ChatId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[ChatsId], [u].[MembersId], [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [UserChats] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [u].[MembersId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[ChatsId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [UserChats] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [u0].[MembersId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ([c].[Id] = [u0].[ChatsId]) AND ([a0].[Id] = @__entity_equality_user_0_Id)) AND ((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Message] AS [m0]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = [m0].[ChatId]) > 0)
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[ChatId], [t0].[CreationDate] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t1].[ChatsId], [t1].[MembersId], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ChatId], [t0].[CreationDate], [t0].[SenderId], [t1].[ChatsId], [t1].[MembersId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AccessFailedCount], [t1].[Avatar], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t1].[Email], [t1].[EmailConfirmed], [t1].[Gender], [t1].[LockoutEnabled], [t1].[LockoutEnd], [t1].[Name], [t1].[NormalizedEmail], [t1].[NormalizedUserName], [t1].[PasswordHash], [t1].[PhoneNumber], [t1].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t1].[SecurityStamp], [t1].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t1].[UserName]
FROM [Chat] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Body], [t].[ChatId], [t].[CreationDate], [t].[SenderId]
    FROM (
        SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Body], [m].[ChatId], [m].[CreationDate], [m].[SenderId], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [m].[ChatId] ORDER BY [m].[CreationDate] DESC) AS [row]
        FROM [Message] AS [m]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[ChatId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[ChatsId], [u].[MembersId], [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [UserChats] AS [u]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [u].[MembersId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[ChatsId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [UserChats] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [u0].[MembersId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE ([c].[Id] = [u0].[ChatsId]) AND ([a0].[Id] = @__entity_equality_user_0_Id)) AND ((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Message] AS [m0]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = [m0].[ChatId]) > 0)
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t0].[ChatId], [t0].[CreationDate] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t1].[ChatsId], [t1].[MembersId], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreationDate], [t].[CreatorId], [t].[Description], [t].[Images], [t].[PostStatusId], [t].[Title], [t].[Id0], [t].[AccessFailedCount], [t].[Avatar], [t].[BirthDate], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[Email], [t].[EmailConfirmed], [t].[Gender], [t].[LockoutEnabled], [t].[LockoutEnd], [t].[Name], [t].[NormalizedEmail], [t].[NormalizedUserName], [t].[PasswordHash], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t].[SecurityStamp], [t].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t].[UserName], [t].[Id1], [t].[CreationDate0], [t].[Title0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CommentBody], [t0].[CreationDate], [t0].[CreatorId], [t0].[PostId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[Avatar], [t0].[BirthDate], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[Email], [t0].[EmailConfirmed], [t0].[Gender], [t0].[LockoutEnabled], [t0].[LockoutEnd], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmail], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[PasswordHash], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[UserName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreationDate], [p].[CreatorId], [p].[Description], [p].[Images], [p].[PostStatusId], [p].[Title], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreationDate] AS [CreationDate0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0]
    FROM [Post] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [p].[CreatorId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CommentBody], [c0].[CreationDate], [c0].[CreatorId], [c0].[PostId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[Avatar], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[Gender], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[Name], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[CreatorId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[PostId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreationDate], [p].[CreatorId], [p].[Description], [p].[Images], [p].[PostStatusId], [p].[Title], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreationDate] AS [CreationDate0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0]

    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CommentBody], [c0].[CreationDate], [c0].[CreatorId], [c0].[PostId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[Avatar], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[Gender], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[Name], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[PostId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreationDate], [p].[CreatorId], [p].[Description], [p].[Images], [p].[PostStatusId], [p].[Title], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Avatar], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[Gender], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreationDate] AS [CreationDate0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0]

    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [p].[CreatorId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Category] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CommentBody], [c0].[CreationDate], [c0].[CreatorId], [c0].[PostId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[Avatar], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[Gender], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[Name], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[CreatorId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[PostId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
